title: MPfree: Star Slinger – Moet & Reese
body:
It’s been a while since we heard from Mancunian beat maestro **Star Slinger**, however that’s not to say he hasn’t been grafting as hard as ever.

Having just finished a full US tour with pals **Shlohmo**, **Shigeto** and **Mux Mool**, Darren’s even found time to drop a beat that he pieced together whilst on the road. _Moet & Reese_ is trademark **Slinger**; wonderfully frenetic and danceable. With his debut single proper _Dumbin’_ released last month, and a remix from **Diplo** on the way, 2012 is going to be another stellar year for SS.

 [Star Slinger – Moet & Reese](http://soundcloud.com/starslingeruk/star-slinger-moet-reese) by [Star Slinger](http://soundcloud.com/starslingeruk)
